title: Frankie's on Fairview
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Opened Jan 2015 this restaurant offers home-style American breakfast, lunch and dinner. Has vegan section featuring tofu scramble, veg-rito, pancakes & waffles, black bean burger, chik'n parm, seitan cheesesteak, meatless meatball parm, and chik'n & waffles. Uses Gardein brand chick'n. Also has vegan desserts.
